-4-2%cf%83-results</guid></item><item><title>宇宙弦是宇宙中的裂缝吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/are-cosmic-strings-cracks-in-the-universe</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 01:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/are-cosmic-strings-cracks-in-the-universe</guid></item><item><title>我们离人类水平的人工智能有多远？这是实现通用人工智能 (AGI) 最合理的时间表</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-close-are-we-to-human-level-ai-heres-the-most-plausible-timeframe-for-achieving-artificial-general-intelligence-agi</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-close-are-we-to-human-level-ai-heres-the-most-plausible-timeframe-for-achieving-artificial-general-intelligence-agi</guid></item><item><title>如果时间不是线性的怎么办？探索宇宙最令人困惑的概念</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-if-time-isnt-linear-exploring-the-universes-most-baffling-concept</link><description>你习惯于将时间视为一条直线：过去在你身后，现在在你脚下，未来在前方无限延伸。时钟滴答作响，日历翻动，你的生活似乎正朝着一个干净的方向前进。但当你开始仔细观察物理学和哲学对时间的实际看法时，这张简单的图景开始以令人惊讶、有时甚至令人不安的方式摇摆不定。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/what-if-time-isnt-linear-exploring-the-universes-most-baffling-concept.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-if-time-isnt-linear-exploring-the-universes-most-baffling-concept</guid></item><item><title>人工神经元成功地与活体脑细胞进行通信</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artificial-neurons-successfully-communicate-with-living-brain-cells</link><description>西北大学的工程师们创造了印刷的人工神经元，它超越了模仿，可以直接与真实的脑细胞相互作用。这些灵活、低成本的设备产生的电信号与活体神经元产生的信号非常相似，使它们能够激活生物脑组织。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/artificial-neurons-successfully-communicate-with-living-brain-cells.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artificial-neurons-successfully-communicate-with-living-brain-cells</guid></item><item><title>我们的宇宙被困在黑洞里了吗？这是科学家的说法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-our-universe-stuck-inside-a-black-hole-heres-what-scientists-say</link><description>黑洞是一种神秘的物体，一种理论认为我们的宇宙存在于黑洞内部。这听起来很奇怪，但有一个令人惊讶的论点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/is-our-universe-stuck-inside-a-black-hole-heres-what-scientists-say.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-our-universe-stuck-inside-a-black-hole-heres-what-scientists-say</guid></item><item><title>Meta 的 TRIBE AI：解码人脑活动的新基础模型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/metas-tribe-ai-a-new-foundation-model-decoding-human-brain-activity</link><description>Meta 的全新 TRIBE AI 模型以 70 倍高分辨率解码大脑活动。了解该基础模型如何使用功能磁共振成像数据来推进计算机神经科学。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/metas-tribe-ai-a-new-foundation-model-decoding-human-brain-activity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 23:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/metas-tribe-ai-a-new-foundation-model-decoding-human-brain-activity</guid></item><item><title>宇宙常数（暗能量）的拓扑起源</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/topological-origin-of-cosmological-constant-dark-energy</link><description>宇宙的形状和宇宙学常数。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/topological-origin-of-cosmological-constant-dark-energy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 23:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/topological-origin-of-cosmological-constant-dark-energy</guid></item></channel></rss>